at about the 3:00 mark you use the term "racist" and "xenophobic"... talk about disinformation... Racist and xenophobic imply hate. Racism and xenophobic are now emotional knee-jerk terms and add no value to the situation.


Please choose your terms more carefully as you will only add to the confusion on the Internet.
